âš™ï¸ Installation & Setup

Clone the repo

git clone https://github.com/karanjoshi-kj/PERSONAL-EXPENSE-TRACKER


Navigate into the project

cd PERSONAL-EXPENSE-TRACKER


Install dependencies

npm install


Run the app

npm start


Build for production

npm run build



